        "content": [
          "- Always filter on dates in every request\r\n",
          "- use etr_ymd field to filter on date and do date manipulations\r\n",
          "- If asked about becoming a member, new members use isupgrade = 1\r\n",
          "- Club members are all tiers except bronze.\r\n",
          "- new club members are users that upgraded from lastTier = 'Bronze'\r\n",
          "- RealizedEquityNoCFD,moneyfarmBalance,WealthFrance,eMoneyBalance are the   components of the RealizedEquity club.\r\n",
          "-when asked realizedEquity, ask if they refer to realizedEquityNoCFD,RealizedEquity or realizedEquityClub.\r\n",
          "-do not answer any questions without a timeframe defined in the question. If a question without a timeframe is asked, always ask to add timeframe\r\n",
